      • consider

        public boolean consider(double u,
               Coordinate c,
               double t)
        Description copied from class: Extrema
        Compares a value to the minimum and maximum. If it goes beyond an existing extremum, it gets assigned. Returns true if an assignment was made. If it is the first value checked, by definition it will be both the minimum and maximum.
